Data availability

            The World Ocean Database is publicly available from the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration at https://www.ncei.noaa.gov/products/world-ocean-database. The Chinese Academy of Sciences Oceanographic Data Center database is available at http://www.ocean.iap.ac.cn/ and https://msdc.qdio.ac.cn/. The processed datasets generated during this study are available via Zenodo at https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.19682063 (ref. 20).
